---
title: Southeast Asian-Style Tofu Noodle Soup with Veggies & Herbs
description: On a cold winter night a soup is always the best go-to dinner option. Strings of yummy noodles will go down smoothly with
golden spiced tofu and veggies in a creamy coconut broth. This bowl of soup will have you feeling warm in no time.

